148
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:01,479
Brilliant crimson. Gold threads embroidered
with hidden python patterns.

149
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,999
Lovebirds and pomegranate designs.

150
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,879
