172
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,959
This one's good!

173
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,160
Hey, Feng Yunqiao!

174
00:09:05,319 --> 00:09:07,038
This one's good!

175
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:08,239
Miss Yunqiao!

176
00:09:08,719 --> 00:09:10,239
- Miss Yunqiao.
- I finally found you.

177
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,680
- Why are you here?
- Feng Yunqiao.

178
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,798
Who are you?

179
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,879
Are you crazy or something?

180
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,518
Miss Yunqiao, let's go home.

181
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:19,959
Go home, okay?

182
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,879
I'm not going home!

183
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,440
- Go home, okay?
- I'm not going home!

184
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,520
- Miss Yunqiao?
- Catch me!

185
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,239
Catch me!

186
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,999
Miss Yunqiao!

187
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,440
Come catch me!

188
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,239
Young Master!

189
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,359
I'll go find Feng Zhilou.

190
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,320
Wait.

191
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,680
You don't look well!

192
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,719
I'll be fine after a bit of rest.

193
00:09:56,439 --> 00:09:57,560
Quickly go.

194
00:10:06,179 --> 00:10:08,240
I really don't understand
what Young Master is thinking.

195
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:10,200
It'd be best
to get Feng Zhilou cure him.

196
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:11,599
Why must we obey

197
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,599
the wishes of mere mortals
and even stand up for her?

198
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,680
Truly ridiculous.

199
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:17,038
Miss Zhilou's life is her own.

200
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:18,518
Whether she wants to cure Young Master

201
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:20,038
is naturally her own decision as well.

202
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:22,079
But if Young Master dies
from the Yang poison,

203
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,359
we will reclaim the sigil,

204
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,719
and she won't live long either.

205
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:30,839
Fei Yuan...

206
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,038
Young Master has defended you
in every way.

207
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,920
What will it take for you
to cure his poison?

208
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,879
Are the minions of the Dragons
always this overbearing?

209
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,359
