are you going to kill me?

210
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,239
Fine.

211
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:42,678
Go ahead

212
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:44,119
and kill me right now.

213
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,638
Anyway, I'm just a loser
who only knows a bit of medicine.

214
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,479
If I die,

215
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,719
your Young Master will suffer

216
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,719
an explosive death too.

217
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:52,080
That way, I won't lose anything at all.
Kill me!

218
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,359
I've never met

219
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:56,079
a woman as unreasonable as you!

220
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,479
You're about to kill me.
I don't have to be reasonable!

221
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,239
Young Master's Yang poison
has never been cured.

222
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,520
Yesterday, for your safety,
he disregarded himself completely.

223
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:04,640
Now, he's giving up
on his own life just for you!

224
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,400
- I...
- Fei Yuan.

225
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:11,119
Young Master,

226
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,558
don't forget your mission.

227
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:13,400
Young Master,

228
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:15,479
Miss Zhilou is your last chance.

229
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,199
How did it become this serious?

230
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,520
You still have the nerve to ask?

231
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:20,318
Young Master broke

232
00:11:20,319 --> 00:11:21,918
into Nie Rongzhi's barrier
to look for you.

233
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:22,839
For the sake of you,

234
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,460
his energy must have been damaged.

235
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:25,680
After dragging it on this long,

236
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,999
