238
00:11:33,319 --> 00:11:34,798
Why won't you, a mere mortal,

239
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:36,199
save Young Master?

240
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,278
Do you know who he is?

241
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:37,759
Shut up,

242
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:38,639
Fei Yuan.

243
00:11:40,439 --> 00:11:41,359
Don't forget,

244
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,678
you're protected by the sigil

245
00:11:42,679 --> 00:11:43,959
because of Young Master.

246
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,199
The sigil was formed
from his most important reverse scale.

247
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:46,959
Actually,

248
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,759
Young Master's power is protecting you.

249
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,759
That's enough.

250
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,639
Whether I can
cure the Yang poison or not,

251
00:11:54,319 --> 00:11:56,320
don't make things difficult
for Feng Zhilou.

252
00:11:57,679 --> 00:11:59,239
If anything happens to me,

253
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,359
the sanctuary...

254
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,639
Enough, Young Master.

255
00:12:03,439 --> 00:12:04,560
If you won't save him,

256
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,359
we'll find a way ourselves.

257
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,680
Who said I won't save him?

258
00:12:31,237 --> 00:12:33,998
♪No one left to lean on♪

259
00:12:33,999 --> 00:12:37,369
♪No way out, no place to run♪

260
00:12:41,562 --> 00:12:44,120
♪Tears held back inside my eyes♪

261
00:12:44,462 --> 00:12:48,382
♪I run against the wind and time♪

262
00:12:52,487 --> 00:12:58,011
♪Loved and lost, regrets remain♪

263
00:12:58,012 --> 00:13:01,281
♪But tears fall down like gentle rain♪

264
00:13:03,162 --> 00:13:09,994
♪I look up strong, I grow with pride♪

265
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,918
(You won't regret it.)

266
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:13,798
♪Living life with heart untied♪

267
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:15,520
(If this drags on any longer,)

268
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:17,111
(you really won't survive tonight.)

269
00:13:17,112 --> 00:13:19,278
♪Holding tight♪

270
00:13:19,279 --> 00:13:20,759
(Even if you don't cure the poison,)

271
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:22,158
(I'll still take you away.)

272
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,711
(I have no regrets.)

273
00:13:24,712 --> 00:13:28,044
♪Healing wounds that fate engraved♪

274
00:13:28,549 --> 00:13:31,274
♪One life to live, one final goal♪

275
00:13:31,275 --> 00:13:34,058
♪I would not ask for love
that shakes the soul♪

276
00:13:34,625 --> 00:13:40,307
♪I only wish fate would echo♪

277
00:14:05,275 --> 00:14:08,345
♪Walls built of prejudice♪

278
00:14:08,575 --> 00:14:12,132
♪Breaking through for light♪

279
00:14:17,225 --> 00:14:20,049
♪Hear the waves of life♪

280
00:14:20,050 --> 00:14:23,882
♪Battling the unpredictability
of the world♪

