00:14:29,125 --> 00:14:34,745
♪Fought, hurt, endured pain,
and tolerated♪

282
00:15:06,362 --> 00:15:08,842
Has the poison been cured?

283
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,800
Thank you, Miss Zhilou.

284
00:15:14,639 --> 00:15:17,200
You and the sigil have an agreement.

285
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,638
Now, only you and I

286
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:20,160
are the masters
of the Canglong Pavilion.

287
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:22,599
Unless we die.

288
00:15:23,559 --> 00:15:24,639
That's why

289
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,879
you value the sigil so much?

290
00:15:29,439 --> 00:15:31,080
Now that my Yang poison has been cured,

291
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,160
I must return to the sanctuary anytime.

292
00:15:33,559 --> 00:15:34,520
From now on,

293
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:36,639
you can rely on martial cultivation.

294
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,040
My spiritual roots...

295
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,800
Your nine spiritual roots
have manifested.

296
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,839
They will activate at the right time,

297
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,479
but that depends on you.

298
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,080
For humans,

299
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:00,839
having spiritual roots
is only the beginning.

300
00:16:01,399 --> 00:16:02,359
Next comes

301
00:16:02,439 --> 00:16:04,200
persistent martial cultivation.

302
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,959
Only through martial cultivation

303
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,959
can you discover your true potential

304
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,280
and unleash it infinitely.

305
00:16:14,279 --> 00:16:15,400
Chu Moshang.

306
00:16:16,919 --> 00:16:18,119
Thank you.

307
00:16:20,279 --> 00:16:22,520
Everything that has happened
these past days

308
00:16:23,639 --> 00:16:25,280
feels like a dream.

309
00:16:26,399 --> 00:16:27,959
It's as if the day before,

310
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:30,040
I was just a useless person with no

311
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:33,839
spiritual roots and martial cultivation
within my family.

312
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,119
I was used,

313
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,119
despised,

314
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,320
and mocked.

315
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:43,280
But now,

316
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,520
because I'm going
to marry into the Dragons,

317
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:48,560
the drinks for the wedding are free,

318
00:16:48,919 --> 00:16:50,560
and I can get the wedding dress easily.

319
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:53,239
It's a treatment I've never

320
00:16:53,519 --> 00:16:54,759
had before.

321
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,280
But what they see

322
00:16:59,159 --> 00:17:00,599
is not me. They only

323
00:17:02,559 --> 00:17:04,080
see the bride of the Dragons.

324
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,239
You don't need to care.

325
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:09,400
Just be yourself.

326
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,879
I want to become strong.

327
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,599
I want martial cultivation.

328
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,599
I want the world

329
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:25,720
to all look up to the name Feng Zhilou.

330
00:17:26,799 --> 00:17:28,320
I must go to Wujing.

331
00:18:13,412 --> 00:18:17,757
(Li Yue, Wujing City Lord)

332
00:18:29,650 --> 00:18:35,424
♪Like petals fall, gone with the clouds♪

333
00:18:35,425 --> 00:18:41,420
♪Like stars fade fast in open skies♪

334
00:18:41,537 --> 00:18:47,236
♪Like snowflakes melting softly
in the evening haze♪

335
00:18:47,237 --> 00:18:53,561
♪Like your fleeting glance
that gave me one brief dream's grace♪

336
00:18:53,562 --> 00:18:59,495
♪Like fireflies flicker
through wild grass, fleeting light♪

337
00:18:59,662 --> 00:19:05,232
♪Like evening breeze
that stirs soft hair in twilight♪

338
00:19:05,512 --> 00:19:11,236
♪Like fleeting thoughts
that surge and then unwind♪

339
00:19:11,237 --> 00:19:17,174
♪Chance meetings fade,
just empty rooms left behind♪

340
00:19:17,175 --> 00:19:22,807
♪You brought a wave
that stirred a wild, restless sea♪

341
00:19:23,087 --> 00:19:28,982
♪Light as a feather,
yet it sank an island deep in me♪

342
00:19:29,162 --> 00:19:35,720
♪In that one moment,
life's grip I couldn't break or sway♪

343
00:19:35,725 --> 00:19:41,482
♪Leaving me lost in memories,
small and fading away♪
